After installation,initialize bash/zsh settings in your $HOME directory and save it.

	$ bashish

You can also configure your theme engine via

	$ bashishtheme

To list all the avaliable theme, do

	$ bashish list

To specficy a theme, do

	$ bashish THEMENAME

To keep it as your default theme after some changes, do

	$ bashish save

For more advanced usage, check bashish man pages via

	$ man bashish
